pthsem for Debian
-----------------

It is a pth library with added semaphore support. It can be used as a replacement of
pth, if pthsem-config is used instead of pth-config.

Additionally pthsem.h instead of pth.h has to be included.
The replacement of AC_CHECK_PTH is called AC_CHECK_PTHSEM

More information availeable at http://www.auto.tuwien.ac.at/~mkoegler/index.php/pth

